flowchart TD
  START([START]) --> PREP[prepare_mode]
  PREP --> RETR[retrieve]
  RETR --> RERANK[rerank]
  RERANK --> DRAFT[draft_answer]
  DRAFT --> VALID[validate_answer]
  VALID --> FINAL[finalize_answer]
  FINAL --> END([END])

  DRAFT -->|mode=reviewer| R0
  DRAFT -->|mode=comparator| C0

  subgraph ReviewerBranch[Reviewer Claim Trial Engine]
    R0[Load reviewer state] --> R1[Normalize or generate attack vectors]
    R1 --> R2[Debate loop]
    R2 --> R3{Synthesis condition met?}
    R3 -->|No| R2
    R3 -->|Yes| R4[Evidence-only judge]
    R4 --> R5[Rewrite compiler card]
    R5 --> R6[Store verdicts and reports]
    R6 --> R7{More vectors?}
    R7 -->|Yes| R2
    R7 -->|No| R8[Build final_report]
  end

  subgraph ComparatorBranch[Comparator Claim Matrix]
    C0[Retrieve per selected paper] --> C1[Merge and dedupe chunks]
    C1 --> C2[Rerank comparator evidence]
    C2 --> C3{Enough evidence?}
    C3 -->|No| C4[Structured comparator fallback]
    C3 -->|Yes| C5[Generate claim-matrix response]
    C5 --> C6[Section-locked comparator output]
    C4 --> C7
    C6 --> C7[Return to shared validate/finalize]
  end

  R8 --> VALID
  C7 --> VALID
